exercise.instructions:
1. Add a variable to @TEMPLATE@_Data_t to store the 'table handle'
    CFE_TBL_Handle_t TblHandle;

Table handles are provided by the cFE and allow apps to access their table data.

1. After the global data @TEMPLATE@_Data is declared add
    static int32 SendTblDataEvent(void);

Note this does not follow the Sample App global function convention. This was doen to show there are options as  described Basecamp's App Dev Guide.

1. In the @TEMPLATE@_Noop() function add
    SendTblDataEvent();

This function is added in the next exercise.
